1. For Loop
2. For Each Loop
3. While Loop
4. Do While Loop

1. For Loop

  for (init variable; boolean expression; update ){
           statement ;
  }

  -Step One .. will initialization of variables .
  -Step Two .. check the boolean condition
  -step three.. update or increase loop counter


  2. For Each Loop

  --Only when you want loop an array...
  for ( type of var : name of array obj){
  statement.....
  }




  3. While loop

  if the boolean expression is true then loop will continue...

  while (boolean expression) {
    statement

  }

  4. Do While loop

  -- this loop will always execute atleast one time..
  --Always write the body of code first and then check the condition..

  do{

  } while (boolean expression);